have Chef Andrew Carmellini here at Google

00:00:05.799 --> 00:00:06.799
New York.

00:00:06.799 --> 00:00:07.799
Welcome.

00:00:07.799 --> 00:00:08.799
&gt;&gt; Andrew: Good to be here.

00:00:08.799 --> 00:00:10.050
Thanks for having me.

00:00:10.050 --> 00:00:13.350
&gt;&gt; Female Interviewer: I'm having this very
James Lipton moment right now.

00:00:13.350 --> 00:00:17.560
"So, tell me about your 12-year-old performance
in

00:00:17.560 --> 00:00:18.560
Annie."

