get a bowl

00:11:26.300 --> 00:11:29.110
of pasta and a glass of wine and split or
you can come on

00:11:29.110 --> 00:11:33.090
Saturday night with your wife or friends or
whoever and

00:11:33.090 --> 00:11:36.510
go crazy or you can just stop by at 6 with
clients.

00:11:36.510 --> 00:11:39.710
I
like that idea restaurants have -- it's like

00:11:39.710 --> 00:11:43.900
a tie to
the community and just becomes all day kind

00:11:43.900 --> 00:11:49.550
of, you know,
just serves like a lot of different needs.

00:11:49.550 --> 00:11:53.310
And it brings
like the crazy energy to it also.

00:11:53.310 --> 00:11:55.322
You know, just kind of
get an eclectic group of people dining there

00:11:55.322 --> 00:11:58.291
for
different reasons and that's what I wanted

00:11:58.291 --> 00:11:59.291
to do at both
restaurants.

